   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">For a program with bundles, you can duplicate the existing bundle structure to create Bundles or Sections with the Sub Category and Exclusions if added. After duplicating a bundle, you can update the product quantity and amount for the new section. You cannot update the number of tiers for the new section. Duplicating a section eliminates the need to re-configure the products in a bundle when you want to provide a discount or a hike for a particular time frame. When you duplicate a section, the start date and end date of the original section is changed to accommodate the contract period.</p>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Duplicating Section functionality is available for the following programs:</p>
      <ul class="- topic/ul ">
         <li class="- topic/li ">Bundle Saving Program</li>
         <li class="- topic/li ">Package Saving Program</li>
      </ul>
